==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: arrow-head
<hw>ar"row-head`</hw></mhw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>,
<pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>the pointed head or striking tip of an
arrow.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <fld>(Bot.)</fld> <def>An aquatic plant of the genus
<gen>Sagittaria</gen>, esp. <spn>Sagittaria sagittifolia</spn>, -- named
from the shape of the leaves.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Arrowheaded</ent>⟦br⟧
